messages.messageBody:
Busy dayS, really.

Tomorrow is pretty solidly booked, and I still haven't caught up on
mail from Friday, so although I'm here a few times a day and mostly to
check on e-mail from home and that... I'm not really paying full
attention to the discussions, and I'm sorry. I wish I could keep up
without missing my time with Holly and getting to hang out with Bea
and her family.

Tomorrow/Saturday, we're all going to Montreal for a get-together,
where Holly and I will speak, and we won't be back until late. Sunday
I go to New Jersey. I might never catch up with this list ever
again; just wanted to let people know that I appear to be here, but
I'm ghostly and weak, e-mailwise...

Sandra
